column1: # DATASET FOR CROP CALCULATIONS. FRUITING SEASON 2019-20
# plant_id: plant name. Plants 328, 333 and 377 are missing, they were not monitored during the this second season (2019-20)
# finalcrop: final crop counted when seed traps were removed.
# collected: number of fruits collected in seed trap (including predated seeds by rodents and green finches)
# collected_no_pred: number of fruits collected in seed trap (not accounting for green finches and rodents)
# n_seedtrap: number of seed traps settled under the plants
# seedtrap_area: area the seed traps occupied under the plant canopy
# canopy_area: area occupied by the plant cannopy measured with Google Earth in m2
